election_record.label: Pennsylvania 1814 Common Council, Philadelphia City

overview.note: The Freeman's Journal and Columbian Chronicle (Philadelphia, PA) from October 13, 1814 lists 2793 votes for William Leedom, 2795 votes for William Lehman, and 2785 votes for Samuel J. Robbins.
